        - english-news-learner: Get and format news articles from English publications (The Economist, Financial Times, etc.) for intermediate ESL learners. Helps with reading comprehension and listening practice. Use this skill whenever the user wants to read news in English for learning purposes, especially from major publications, or wants news formatted for English study with vocabulary explanations and translations.
        - 来点选题: 当用户视频创作选题枯竭的时候，为用户提供选题思路
